\fs45 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Model Selection :\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs32 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 New techniques for distillation, quantization, and synthetic data generation are enabling compact models to inherit surprising levels of capability from their larger counterparts.\
\
how do you choose the right model for your agentic system? The truth is, there isn\'92t a one-size-fits-all answer. In fact, one of the most reasonable starting points is simply to use the latest general-purpose model from a leading provider like OpenAI or Anthropic\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa480\parhyphenfactor20\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 That said, they\'a0aren\'92t always the most efficient choice. For many tasks\'97especially those that are well-defined, low-latency, or cost-sensitive\'97much smaller models can provide near-equivalent performance at a fraction of the cost. This has led to a growing trend: automated model selection. Some\'a0platforms now route simpler queries to fast, inexpensive small models, reserving the large, expensive models for more complex reasoning. This dynamic test-time optimization is proving effective, and it hints at a future where multimodel systems become the norm.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa640\partightenfactor0

\fs45 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 From Synchronous to Asynchronous Operations\

\fs32 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 In contrast, autonomous agents are designed for\'a0asynchronous operation unlike software systems . They can manage multiple tasks in parallel, swiftly adapt to new information, and prioritize actions dynamically based on changing conditions. This asynchronous processing dramatically enhances efficiency, reducing idle time and optimizing the use of computational resources.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Rather than spending time on repetitive or mechanical steps, individuals can focus on strategic oversight, review, and high-value decision making\'97amplifying human creativity and judgment while letting agents handle the operational details. These agents make it much easier for human roles to be proactive\'a0rather than reactive.
\f2\i \cf2 \cb1 \strokec2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\i0 \cf2 \strokec2 \
