\fs45 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Principles for Building Effective Agentic Systems\
\pard\pardeftab720\parhyphenfactor20\partightenfactor0

\f2\i\fs32 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Scalability\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa480\parhyphenfactor20\partightenfactor0

\f1\i0 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Ensure that\'a0agents can handle growing workloads and diverse tasks by utilizing distributed architectures, cloud-based infrastructure, and efficient algorithms that support parallel processing and resource optimization.\cf2 \cb1 \strokec2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\parhyphenfactor20\partightenfactor0

\f2\i \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Modularity\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa480\parhyphenfactor20\partightenfactor0

\f1\i0 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Design\'a0agents with independent, interchangeable components connected through clear interfaces. This modular approach simplifies maintenance, promotes flexibility, and facilitates rapid adaptation to new requirements or technologies.\cf2 \cb1 \strokec2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\parhyphenfactor20\partightenfactor0

\f2\i \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Continuous learning\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa480\parhyphenfactor20\partightenfactor0

\f1\i0 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Equip\'a0agents with mechanisms to learn from experience, such as in-context learning. Integrate user feedback to refine agent behaviors and maintain\'a0performance\'a0relevance as tasks evolve.\cf2 \cb1 \strokec2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\parhyphenfactor20\partightenfactor0

\f2\i \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Resilience\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa480\parhyphenfactor20\partightenfactor0

\f1\i0 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Develop robust\'a0resilience architectures capable of gracefully handling errors, security threats, timeouts, and unexpected conditions.\cf2 \cb1 \strokec2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\parhyphenfactor20\partightenfactor0

\f2\i \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Future-proofing\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa480\parhyphenfactor20\partightenfactor0

\f1\i0 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Build agent\'a0systems around open standards and scalable infrastructure, fostering a culture of innovation to adapt quickly to emerging technologies and evolving user expectations\cf2 \cb1 \strokec2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa640\partightenfactor0

